{"text_id":121370,"tokens":["An","omaly"," detection"," is"," a"," challenging"," problem"," in"," intelligent"," video"," surveillance","."," Most"," existing"," methods"," are"," computation","-","consuming",","," which"," cannot"," satisfy"," the"," real","-","time"," requirement","."," In"," this"," paper",","," we"," propose"," a"," real","-","time"," anomaly"," detection"," Two","-","stage"," anomaly"," detection"," is"," a"," useful"," technique"," for"," video"," surveillance","."," In"," the"," first"," stage",","," the"," video"," sequence"," is"," segmented"," into"," regions"," of"," interest"," (","RO","Is",")"," according"," to"," pre","-","defined"," criteria","."," In"," the"," second"," stage",","," the"," abnormalities"," are"," detected"," by"," comparing"," the"," detected"," regions"," with"," a"," database"," of"," normal"," video"," frames","."," Experimental"," results"," demonstrate"," that"," our"," proposed"," method"," achieves"," good"," performance"," in"," both"," the"," first"," and"," second"," stages","."],"sub_source":"sci_gen","model":"t0_11b","label":1}